{#
MESSAGE: Low Battery Alert - Telegram
PARAMETERS:
  - device_name: Name of the device (string)
  - battery_level: Current battery level (float)
  - threshold: Low battery threshold (float)
  - timestamp: Alert timestamp (datetime)
#}
{% macro low_battery_alert_telegram(device_name, battery_level, threshold, timestamp) %}
🟡 *LOW BATTERY ALERT*

⚠️ *Device Battery Running Low*

📱 *Device:* {{ device_name }}
🔋 *Battery Level:* {{ battery_level | round(1) }}%
📊 *Threshold:* {{ threshold | round(1) }}%

💡 *Action Required:*
• Order replacement battery
• Plan battery replacement soon
• Monitor device functionality

🏠 System: 192.168.1.30:8123
📅 {{ timestamp.strftime('%A, %d %B %Y %H:%M') }}
{% endmacro %}

