  - timestamp: Report timestamp (datetime)
#}
{% macro prepaid_meter_status_telegram(units_left, daily_usage, days_remaining, warning_threshold, critical_threshold, emergency_threshold, timestamp) %}
⚡ *PREPAID METER DAILY STATUS*

📊 *Current Balance:*
🔋 Units Remaining: {{ units_left | round(1) }} kWh

📈 *Usage Statistics:*
📅 Yesterday: {{ daily_usage | round(2) }} kWh
⏱️ Days Remaining: ~{{ days_remaining | round(1) }} days

🎯 *Alert Thresholds:*
🟡 Warning: {{ warning_threshold | round(0) }} kWh
🟠 Critical: {{ critical_threshold | round(0) }} kWh
🔴 Emergency: {{ emergency_threshold | round(0) }} kWh

{% if units_left < critical_threshold %}⚠️ *ACTION REQUIRED* - Balance is critically low!
{% elif units_left < warning_threshold %}⚠️ Consider recharging soon
{% else %}✅ Balance is healthy
{% endif %}

📅 {{ timestamp.strftime('%A, %d %B %Y') }}
{% endmacro %}

